PrecisAuthority to (a) enter into a SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT with the DUNCAN'S BAND for the purpose of resolving a specific claim involving the 1928 surrender for sale of some 160 acres of land fronting on Bear Lake in Alberta, formerly known as Louison Cardinal Indian Reserve No. 151H, and (b) to accept the Instrument of Absolute Surrender set out in Article 4 thereof.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to (a) enter into a SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT with the DUNCAN'S BAND
for the purpose of resolving a specific claim involving the 1928 surrender
for sale of some 160 acres of land fronting on Bear Lake in Alberta,
formerly known as Louison Cardinal Indian Reserve No. 151H, and (b) to
accept the Instrument of Absolute Surrender set out in Article 4 thereof.
